---
import Portrait from "../../assets/antoine-bourchardy.png";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<section class="container max-w-[760px] py-10 text-center sm:py-20">
  <h2
    class="text-h3 sm:text-h2 font-medium"
  >
    Why are we open source?
  </h2>
  <p
    class="text-quote-sm sm:text-quote text-muted-foreground my-10 sm:my-12"
  >
    “Nobody should pay for a glorified excel template. GRC is about connexion and extensibility - everyone has a unique way of working, being OSS allows them to extend what we are building."
  </p>
  <Image
    densities={[1, 2]}
    class="mx-auto mb-10 block sm:mb-12"
    src={Portrait}
    alt="Portrait of Antoine Bouchardy"
    width={164}
    height={164}
  />
  <p class="text-muted-foreground">— Antoine Bouchardy, Co-founder & CEO</p>
</section>
